entry.title: Using scribe to write online meeting summaries
entry.content:
Use case:

When you are in a skype chat session for a meeting it is convenient to capture the meeting notes from the chat session.

Environments as IRC have something like meeting bot to handle this.

For Skype I found

https://bitbucket.org/mhall/pyskypescribe
